category: Text Doc
requires: python xmlto
sdesc: "Text-based document generation tool"
ldesc: "AsciiDoc is a text document format for writing short documents,
articles, books and UNIX man pages. AsciiDoc files can be translated to
HTML and DocBook markups using the asciidoc(1) command.

AsciiDoc is highly configurable: both the AsciiDoc source file syntax
and the backend output markups (which can be almost any type of SGML/XML
markup) can be customized and extended by the user."
